our seeds  biotechnology trait products  and herbicides provide farmers with solutions that improve productivity  reduce the costs of farming  and produce better foods for consumers and better feed for animals 
we manage our business in two segments seeds and genomics and agricultural productivity 
through our seeds and genomics segment  we produce leading seed brands  including dekalb  asgrow  seminis and stoneville  and we develop biotechnology traits that assist farmers in controlling insects and weeds 
